    "long_instructions": "## Interior Design\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan out ideas for decorating a room.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Look at the images already uploaded to this level and decide if you'd like to use those or images of a room more relevant to you.\r\n2. Decide on new areas you'd like to come up with ideas for. Here are some common topics:\r\n\t- Furniture & Layout\r\n    - Lighting\r\n    - Color & Walls\r\n    - Texture & Fabrics\r\n    - Decor & Accessories\r\n    - Technology & Smart Features\r\n    - You can use AI chat to help you brainstorm more ideas if you'd like!\r\n3. Add the images you want to include in your input to your prompt.\r\n4. **Copy and paste** the following prompt:\r\n\r\n>Help me brainstorm ideas around [insert area of interest here] in this room.\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. Change and add to your prompt to see if you can get AI Chat to provide you more useful responses.\r\n",
